msgstr "# triton.language.flip"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/flip.md:2
msgid "## 1. 函数概述"
msgstr "## 1. Function Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/flip.md:4
msgid "简介：将tensor沿某一维度进行翻转。"
msgstr "Introduction: Flip the tensor along a certain dimension."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/flip.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.flip(x, dim=None)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/flip.md:8
msgid "## 2. 规格"
msgstr "## 2. Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/flip.md:10
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/flip.md:12
msgid ""
"| 参数名           | 类型                | 说明                                                             |\n"
"| ------------- | ----------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------- |\n"
"| `x`        | `tensor`          | 张量数据                                                      |\n"
"| `dim`        | `int`          | 整型                                                      |\n"
"| `_semantic`   | -                 | 保留参数，暂不支持外部调用\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter Name | Type      | Description                                      |\n"
"| ------------- | --------- | ------------------------------------------------ |\n"
"| `x`           | `tensor`  | Tensor data                                      |\n"
"| `dim`         | `int`     | Integer                                          |\n"
"| `_semantic`   | -         | Reserved parameter, external calls not supported |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/flip.md:14
msgid ""
"返回值：\n"
"`out`：输出张量的shape与输入x的shape相同\n"
msgstr ""
"Return value:  \n"
"`out`: The shape of the output tensor is the same as the shape of the input `x`.\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/flip.md:16
msgid "### 2.2 OP 规格"
msgstr "### 2.2 OP Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/flip.md:18
msgid "#### 2.2.1 DataType 支持"
msgstr "#### 2.2.1 DataType Support"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/flip.md:20
msgid ""
"|        | int8 | int16 | int32 | uint8 | uint16 | uint32 | uint64 | int64 | fp16 | fp32 | fp64 | bf16 | bool |\n"
"| ------ | ---- | ----- | ----- | ----- | ------ | ------ | ------ | ----- | ---- | ---- | ---- | ---- | ---- |\n"
"| GPU    | √     | √      | √     | √      |  √      |  √       |  √       | √      | √    | √   | √    | √    | √    |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | √    | √     | √     | √     | ×     | ×      | ×      | √     | √    | √    | ×    | √    | √    |\n"
msgstr ""
"|        | int8 | int16 | int32 | uint8 | uint16 | uint32 | uint64 | int64 | fp16 | fp32 | fp64 | bf16 | bool |\n"
"| ------ | ---- | ----- | ----- | ----- | ------ | ------ | ------ | ----- | ---- | ---- | ---- | ---- | ---- |\n"
"| GPU    | √     | √      | √     | √      |  √      |  √       |  √       | √      | √    | √   | √    | √    | √    |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | √    | √     | √     | √     | ×     | ×      | ×      | √     | √    | √    | ×    | √    | √    |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/flip.md:22
msgid "结论：Ascend 相比 GPU 缺失 uint、fp64 类型支持。"
msgstr "Conclusion: Ascend lacks support for uint and fp64 types compared to GPU."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/flip.md:24
msgid "#### 2.2.2 Shape 支持"
msgstr "#### 2.2.2 Shape Support"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/flip.md:26
msgid ""
"|            | 支持维度范围        |\n"
"| ---------- | ------------------- |\n"
"| GPU        | 仅支持 1~5维 tensor |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | 仅支持 1~5维 tensor |\n"
msgstr ""
"|            | Supported Dimension Range |\n"
"| ---------- | ----------------------- |\n"
"| GPU        | Only supports 1~5D tensors |\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | Only supports 1~5D tensors |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/flip.md:28
msgid "结论：在 Shape 方面，GPU 与 Ascend 平台无差异，均支持 1 至 5 维张量。"
msgstr "Conclusion: In terms of Shape, there is no difference between GPU and Ascend platforms; both support tensors from 1 to 5 dimensions."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/flip.md:30
msgid "### 2.3 特殊限制说明"
msgstr "### 2.3 Special Restrictions"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/flip.md:32
msgid "> 相对社区能力缺失且无法实现"
msgstr "Relative community capability is lacking and cannot be achieved."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/flip.md:34
msgid "Ascend 相比 GPU 缺失 uint、fp64 类型支持。"
msgstr "Ascend lacks support for uint and fp64 types compared to GPU."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/flip.md:36
msgid "### 2.4 使用方法"
msgstr "### 2.4 Usage"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/flip.md:38
msgid "以下示例将输入张量 `x` 沿指定维度进行翻转："
msgstr "The following example flips the input tensor `x` along the specified dimension:"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Indexing_Ops/flip.md:40
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"@triton.jit\n"
"def fn_npu_3d(output_ptr, x_ptr, XB: tl.constexpr, YB: tl.constexpr, ZB: tl.constexpr, XNUMEL: tl.constexpr,\n"
"            YNUMEL: tl.constexpr, ZNUMEL: tl.constexpr):\n"
"    xidx = tl.arange(0, XB) + tl.program_id(0) * XB\n"
"    yidx = tl.arange(0, YB) + tl.program_id(1) * YB\n"
"    zidx = tl.arange(0, ZB) + tl.program_id(2) * ZB\n"
"    idx = xidx[:, None, None] * YNUMEL * ZNUMEL + yidx[None, :, None] * ZNUMEL + zidx[None, None, :]\n"
"    X = tl.load(x_ptr + idx)\n"
"    ret = tl.flip(X, 2)\n"
"    oidx = xidx[:, None, None] * YNUMEL * ZNUMEL + yidx[None, :, None] * ZNUMEL + zidx[None, None, :]\n"
"    tl.store(output_ptr + oidx, ret)\n"
"\n"
"x = test_common.generate_tensor(shape, dtype).npu()\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

